<a name="josef-hoffmann" class="anchor" href="#josef-hoffmann"><span class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>
<h1>Melon Service by Josef Hoffmann</h1>
<p>
The "Melon Service" of Josef Hoffmann is a tea service for two people.
The service is based on simple curves replicated to perceive a greater roundness.
The simplicity of the curves has allowed me to develop the whole service
The "Melon Service" consists of a jug, a teapot, a sugar bowl and two cups.</p>

<h2><a href="http://stederob.github.io/Final-Project/carafe.html">Carafe</a></h2>
The carafe is given by most verticals curves of different heights.
<p><img src="https://github.com/stederob/Final-Project/blob/gh-pages/images/melon%20service/js-carafe.png?raw=true" alt="carafe-js" style="width:300px; heigth:30px;"></p>
<h2><a href="http://stederob.github.io/Final-Project/teapot.html">Teapot</a></h2>
The teapot is made ​​up of several concentric curves that give the different depths.
<p><img src="https://github.com/stederob/Final-Project/blob/gh-pages/images/melon%20service/teapot-js.png?raw=true" alt="teapot-js" style="width:300px; heigth:30px;"></p>
<h2><a href="http://stederob.github.io/Final-Project/sugarbowl.html">Sugar Bowl</a></h2>
The sugar is almost spherical if it were not for the sector occupied by the cover.
<p><img src="https://github.com/stederob/Final-Project/blob/gh-pages/images/melon%20service/js-sugarbowl.png?raw=true" alt="sugar-bowl-js" style="width:300px; heigth:30px;"></p>
<h2><a href="http://stederob.github.io/Final-Project/cup.html">Cup</a></h2>
The cups show their sophistication  with petal-shaped saucers.
<p><img src="https://github.com/stederob/Final-Project/blob/gh-pages/images/melon%20service/js-cup.png?raw=true" alt="sugar-bowl-js" style="width:300px; heigth:30px;"></p>

This is the final result.

<p><img src="https://github.com/stederob/Final-Project/blob/gh-pages/images/melone_design.jpg?raw=true" style="width:290px; heigth:290px;">
<img src="https://github.com/stederob/Final-Project/blob/gh-pages/images/melon%20service/melon-service.png?raw=true" alt="Josef Hoffmann" style="width:310px; heigth:310px;"></p>
